    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09023">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1787-02-20">1787 г. 20 февраля.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Пришли ко мне фальшивую ассигнацию, присланную из <placeName ref="places.xml#pet01">Питербурга</placeName>
                <note type="editorial">
                    More explanation to this case is provided in A.V. Khrapovitskii's diary, which mentions <date when-custom="1787-02-20">on the same day</date> the report on <persName ref="people.xml#sum02">horse guard cornet Sumarokov</persName> and sergeant-majors <persName ref="people.xml#rom06">Romberg</persName> and <persName ref="people.xml#kun01">Kunitskii</persName>, who were accused of forging new banknotes in amount of 450 rubles (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#dnevni02">Dnevnik A.V. Khrapovitskago s 18 ianvaria 1782 po 17 sentiabria 1793 goda</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 15.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>;
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#panche01">Slovar' russkikh pisatelei 18 veka</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 202.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>.</p>
        </body>
